Policykit
  - Necessary for installing the kindlegen binary to the /usr/bin directory on demand
  - Necessary for mounting e-readers and copying files

Need a *.policykit file to be installed to /usr/share/polkit-1/actions on program install (meson)

Some sort of bottleneck in the GreetingView. Withoutit the library loads lag-free, but with it, any change to the library makes the top left library count load late and freezes the entire window.